kernel.h: unconditionally include asm/div64.h for do_div()

Include asm/div64.h for do_div() usage in DIV_ROUND_DOWN_ULL() and
DIV_ROUND_CLOSEST_ULL().  Remove the old CONFIG_LBDAF=y conditional
include.

